<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I have been thinking a lot, these days, about =
<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29838293.272550/aH=
R0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMDktMjQvZWFyb=
